  "text": "To date, 400 loci associated with T2D risk have been identified [CITATION_1] . Genome-wide association studies in African American and European populations identified one T2D locus associated to HLA-B, coding for major histocompatibility complex class I [CITATION_2] . Because there is long-range linkage disequilibrium in this region the causality of HLA-B remains uncertain [CITATION_3] .",
